Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高畑老师…涅吉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬了涅吉老师的星水晶去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这魔法世界就是为星水晶所创造
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之也就是说  魔法世界本身便是星水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星水晶 = 魔法世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说星水晶是形成这个世界的核心更容易为人所接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错呢  叶加濑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此…原来如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听明白了么  小古？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  似乎很多人都没听明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同甘共苦的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那算哪门子的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏美其实也没听明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？  我…我听明白了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏美只要一撒谎  身形就会小一号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来就不高嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  高畑老师  现在还不能了解涅吉弟弟的状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万一受伤了可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？  不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隆道  想办法探察一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,探察状况吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！  森林居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙！  …涅佳涅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总算没事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过隆道和涅佳涅大姐忙着布结界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就没人可以探察大哥的状况了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？  怎么可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文洁琳呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！  对啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文也会施展吟唱魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  伊文  拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人已经和涅吉老师订立了临时契约
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在此不正应该给予协助么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…别提临时契约的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  伊文同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是明日菜大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,lic lac la lac lilac
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紧闭的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遮掩的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寄予一缕光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现其形于吾面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,la lac spiritus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有画面了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平安无事实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  我们也在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢  怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影  冒牌货  廉价物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎涅吉老师尚未察觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨涅吉  真正的我们在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的声音是无法传到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文  想办法让他能够听到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得轻松！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边究竟发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是要试图欺骗涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是阴谋么…  涅吉小弟  要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  这里好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深不见底呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道下面怎样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…现在即使在上方四处逃散也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼  你下去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有魔杖么  快去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「时空冥界」…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于魔法世界的黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若涅吉老师被卷入其中…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意为大家去调查一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是班主任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别再彷徨  为了你的学生毫不犹豫地去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是一大群呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快去！  这里交给我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹我也是A班的学生  不希望看见班上同学为此受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  刚才的话你都听见了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文死也不会说这种话的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那爽朗的笑容  简直不现实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快回忆起真正的伊文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆起蛮不讲理到极点  无论何时都冷若冰霜的货真价实的伊文！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！  别乱动！  影像都看不清啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还在发什么呆  赶快啊  小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…你不是伊文洁琳同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…大家也同样都是冒牌货！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀  涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说那么让人伤心的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗不了我的  你们不是我的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是幻影！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…还是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…被识破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…内部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:08:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…光凭你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:08:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…从
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,tel ma amorista
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了…茶茶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得那么绝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你刚才的一席话而深受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪明日菜说伊文「死也不会说」那种话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「蛮不讲理到极点  无论何时都冷若冰霜」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…的确有些过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…什么嘛  可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是星水晶创造的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么傻话  我可不是冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  你不是我熟识的阿妮亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱哭鬼一点儿也没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在森林里迷路的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳落山了  涅吉便大哭起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉总是哭个不停  我就把糖果送给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是阿妮亚！
